"privacy_title" = "Shinsou Privacy Policy";
"privacy_last_updated" = "Last updated: March 14, 2026";
"privacy_intro" = "Thank you for choosing Shinsou. We value your privacy and have designed this app with a \"privacy-first\" and \"data stays local\" approach.";
"privacy_section1_title" = "1. Data Collection & Usage";
"privacy_section1_body" = "This app is an open-source media reading tool. We do not actively collect any personally identifiable information.\n\nReading History & Library: All your manga lists, reading progress, and favorites are stored solely on your local device. We have no central server and cannot access, store, or leak your reading preferences.\n\nAccount Information: No account registration is required. If you link third-party services (e.g. tracking sites), that information is only used to complete sync functionality. We do not obtain login credentials for those services.";
"privacy_section2_title" = "2. External Extensions";
"privacy_section2_body" = "This app does not provide any content itself. Content is obtained through extensions you install.\n\nThird-party Sources: When you use extensions to browse content, your IP address and other network information are sent directly to the content source website.\n\nRisk Notice: Each content source has its own privacy policy. We cannot control their behavior and recommend you stay vigilant when using specific sources.";
"privacy_section3_title" = "3. Permissions";
"privacy_section3_body" = "To ensure proper functionality, we may request the following permissions:\n\nStorage: To store downloaded manga content and backup data.\n\nNetwork Access: To download content, update extensions, and sync data.";
"privacy_section4_title" = "4. Data Security & Backup";
"privacy_section4_body" = "Since data is stored locally, this app does not have cloud recovery capabilities. If you delete the app without performing a manual backup, your data will be permanently lost. We strongly recommend regularly using the export backup feature.";
"privacy_section5_title" = "5. Policy Updates";
"privacy_section5_body" = "We may update this policy from time to time. We recommend checking periodically. Continued use of this app constitutes acceptance of this policy.";
"about_footer" = "Made with ❤️ by the Shinsou community";

